Peter Pan gain Challenger +1. (They get +1 ¤
while challenging.)

SIGNS OF LIFE When you play this character,
if you have another Alien character in play,
draw a card.

FOLLOW THE CLUES Banish this item — Chosen
character gains Alert this turn. (They can challenge as
if they had Evasive.)

ARM YOURSELF 1 ⬡, Banish this item — Chosen
character gains Challenger +3 this turn. (They get +3 ¤
while challenging.)

